snippet.title: Queen Fighter 2000 (女王格鬥2000) Bootleg [GBC]
snippet.description: Queen Fighter 2000, also known as Gals Fighters and Queen of Fighting 2000, is an unlicensed Game Boy Color game produced in 2000 by Vast Fame. It's an all-female fighting game based off of SNK's Gals' Fighters title for the Neo Geo Pocket Color and is Vast Fame's first "original" fighter (their previous one, Super Fighters S, is a hack of an official The King of Fighters game.) Source: https://bootleggames.fandom.com/wiki/Queen_Fighter_2000
